  "content": "\n                <p><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"1S02A2\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QSBwYXRob2xvZ2ljYWwgaGFyZGVuaW5nIG9mIHRpc3N1ZSBhcyBhIHJlc3VsdCBvZiBhbiBpbmZsYW1tYXRvcnkgb3IgYSBkZWdlbmVyYXRpdmUgcHJvY2Vzcy4gQ2hhcmFjdGVyaXplZCBoaXN0b2xvZ2ljYWxseSBieSBhbiBpbmNyZWFzZSBpbiB0aGUgbGV2ZWwgb2YgY29sbGFnZW4gYW5kL29yIHJldGljdWxpbi48L3A+\" id=\"Lcaf6f7798cbaa454c2bd50ba39bc11c7\" data-source=\"Lcaf6f7798cbaa454c2bd50ba39bc11c7\">Sclerosing</span> mesenteritis is an uncommon <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"lj0v0T\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QSBkZXNjcmlwdG9yIGZvciBhIGNvbmRpdGlvbiB3aXRoIGFuIHVua25vd24gY2F1c2Ugb3IgcGF0aG9waHlzaW9sb2d5LjwvcD4=\" id=\"L14187b8b310af291e81dae0c673201a6\" data-source=\"L14187b8b310af291e81dae0c673201a6\">idiopathic</span> autoimmune condition characterized by inflammation, <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"bZbHZH\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z70a8756809acc19ae6b8afd9344634f0\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-lxid=\"VP0GdT\" data-section-id=\"R9clMe0\" data-sxid=\"R9clMe0\" data-title=\"Q2VsbHVsYXIgY2hhbmdlcyBhbmQgYWRhcHRpdmUgcmVzcG9uc2VzIOKGkiBOZWNyb3Npcw==\" id=\"L3251c3e115380b85505e6c4892febe4e\" data-source=\"L3251c3e115380b85505e6c4892febe4e\">fat necrosis</span>, and <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"yi0d8f\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zf29b9e7e01bf75d0402e969b50992d30\" data-learningcard-id=\"ro0fWS\" data-lxid=\"ro0fWS\" data-section-id=\"H9cKKe0\" data-sxid=\"H9cKKe0\" data-title=\"Q29ubmVjdGl2ZSB0aXNzdWUg4oaSIENsaW5pY2FsIHNpZ25pZmljYW5jZQ==\" id=\"L1be78b1e27bd01b3e3b2f2590e2186d8\" data-source=\"L1be78b1e27bd01b3e3b2f2590e2186d8\">fibrosis</span> of the bowel <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"xjXEcy\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z2e7145689ecdf9560060a209d9ae676a\" data-learningcard-id=\"LJ0wuS\" data-lxid=\"LJ0wuS\" data-section-id=\"Ja1sl20\" data-sxid=\"Ja1sl20\" data-title=\"QWJkb21pbmFsIGNhdml0eSDihpIgUGVyaXRvbmV1bQ==\" id=\"Ldb0a4edfa287ebeb2466a73a63c278b5\" data-source=\"Ldb0a4edfa287ebeb2466a73a63c278b5\">mesentery</span>. Many patients are asymptomatic; in symptomatic patients, abdominal <span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zd673a3f7ee36023aab5a267899e984cc\" data-learningcard-id=\"xN0EWg\" data-lxid=\"xN0EWg\" data-section-id=\"NBX-a00\" data-sxid=\"NBX-a00\" data-title=\"UHJpbmNpcGxlcyBvZiBwYWluIG1hbmFnZW1lbnQg4oaSIENsYXNzaWZpY2F0aW9uIG9mIHBhaW4=\" id=\"Lcf5baefa6487b283ff6b8ab8c1c3336c\" data-source=\"Lcf5baefa6487b283ff6b8ab8c1c3336c\">pain</span> is most common. The diagnosis is increasingly made incidentally via CT imaging, which characteristically shows intestine displaced by a hazy <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"xjXEcy\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z2e7145689ecdf9560060a209d9ae676a\" data-learningcard-id=\"LJ0wuS\" data-lxid=\"LJ0wuS\" data-section-id=\"Ja1sl20\" data-sxid=\"Ja1sl20\" data-title=\"QWJkb21pbmFsIGNhdml0eSDihpIgUGVyaXRvbmV1bQ==\" id=\"Lcaf64b78385b9a31fbce0fb195ad1f03\" data-source=\"Lcaf64b78385b9a31fbce0fb195ad1f03\">mesenteric</span> fat mass, also known as “misty <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"xjXEcy\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z2e7145689ecdf9560060a209d9ae676a\" data-learningcard-id=\"LJ0wuS\" data-lxid=\"LJ0wuS\" data-section-id=\"Ja1sl20\" data-sxid=\"Ja1sl20\" data-title=\"QWJkb21pbmFsIGNhdml0eSDihpIgUGVyaXRvbmV1bQ==\" id=\"L3a5d095a25f2c669591900997cf352ee\" data-source=\"L3a5d095a25f2c669591900997cf352ee\">mesentery</span>.” A presumptive diagnosis is often possible; <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"sebtZG\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+VGhlIHJlbW92YWwgb2YgY2VsbHMgb3IgdGlzc3VlIGZvciBsYWJvcmF0b3J5IGV4YW1pbmF0aW9uIG9yIHRlc3RpbmcuIFNldmVyYWwgbWV0aG9kcyBleGlzdCB0byByZW1vdmUgdGhlIHRhcmdldCB0aXNzdWUgKGUuZy4sIGZpbmUgbmVlZGxlIGFzcGlyYXRpb24sIHB1bmNoIGJpb3BzeSkuPC9wPg==\" id=\"L4e985472b34422ca67b2c97bf03c4aba\" data-source=\"L4e985472b34422ca67b2c97bf03c4aba\">biopsy</span> is indicated if there are features concerning for <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"OHXIqz\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z8c3bce39ca977e0f872b6d9fb3be8cfb\" data-learningcard-id=\"WM0Png\" data-lxid=\"WM0Png\" data-section-id=\"azXQr00\" data-sxid=\"azXQr00\" data-title=\"R2VuZXJhbCBvbmNvbG9neSDihpIgTm9tZW5jbGF0dXJl\" id=\"Le2de6e16f25b35094f8ead9142758633\" data-source=\"Le2de6e16f25b35094f8ead9142758633\">malignancy</span> or <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"pwcLPe0\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z6709f19b0cddb8847d2d6ffe04719c2b\" data-learningcard-id=\"Vu0GJ3\" data-lxid=\"Vu0GJ3\" data-title=\"SWdHNC1yZWxhdGVkIGRpc2Vhc2U=\" id=\"Lb11158f91b2f1c622e5df1b126accedb\" data-source=\"Lb11158f91b2f1c622e5df1b126accedb\">IgG4-related disease</span>. Treatment of symptoms typically involves immunomodulatory drugs (e.g., <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"3faSNP\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z62c2028efe014cd4faaf82ccb312cd4c\" data-learningcard-id=\"uk0ppT\" data-lxid=\"uk0ppT\" data-section-id=\"a_1Q5j0\" data-sxid=\"a_1Q5j0\" data-title=\"RmVtYWxlIHNleCBob3Jtb25lcyDihpIgUmVwcm9kdWN0aXZlIHN5c3RlbSBkcnVncw==\" id=\"L829a52671c207f8f9f209404c1f3ae23\" data-source=\"L829a52671c207f8f9f209404c1f3ae23\">tamoxifen</span>, <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"4L03Bg\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z521ecba6f9748e7fed6b743a73ccfabd\" data-learningcard-id=\"km0mfg\" data-lxid=\"km0mfg\" data-title=\"R2x1Y29jb3J0aWNvaWRz\" id=\"L40911f256fa2c428f7ac51365ef93c08\" data-source=\"L40911f256fa2c428f7ac51365ef93c08\">glucocorticoids</span>). <span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Za68e01313423572283ce418087f356cb\" data-learningcard-id=\"7I04Vh\" data-lxid=\"7I04Vh\" data-section-id=\"w41hlS0\" data-sxid=\"w41hlS0\" data-title=\"U3VyZ2VyeSBjbGVya3NoaXAg4oaSIFN1cmdlcnkgb3ZlcnZpZXc=\" id=\"Lf5b3884ad02e5b2bbe68ac702e102035\" data-source=\"Lf5b3884ad02e5b2bbe68ac702e102035\">Surgery</span> is reserved for patients with <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"2O0T7T\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zd632dab0bd82fad268f38b319729e1c3\" data-learningcard-id=\"230T3f\" data-lxid=\"230T3f\" data-title=\"Qm93ZWwgb2JzdHJ1Y3Rpb24=\" id=\"Laea970f627fbacd17b7aefe51a9abd52\" data-source=\"Laea970f627fbacd17b7aefe51a9abd52\">bowel obstruction</span> and is not curative. Most patients show no disease progression after <span class=\"nowrap\">2 years</span> of follow-up.</p>\n<!--no-condensed--><ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>Mean age of patients: <span class=\"nowrap\">55 years</span>\n</li>\n<li><span class=\"nowrap\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"ef0xO2\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+VGhlIHN5bWJvbCBmb3IgdGhlIG1hbGUgc2V4LjwvcD4=\" id=\"Ld355300a925f8908cc4695df7dc45ac6\" data-source=\"Ld355300a925f8908cc4695df7dc45ac6\">♂</span> &gt; <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"Vf0GO2\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+VGhlIHN5bWJvbCBmb3IgdGhlIGZlbWFsZSBzZXguPC9wPg==\" id=\"L84c3c4a1216db93b5b138c08696e976f\" data-source=\"L84c3c4a1216db93b5b138c08696e976f\">♀</span></span></li>\n<li>Most common in White individuals</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"unwichtig\">Epidemiological data refers to the US, unless otherwise specified.</span></p>\n<!--no-condensed--><ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>The exact cause is not fully understood.</li>\n<li>Generally considered an <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"lj0v0T\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QSBkZXNjcmlwdG9yIGZvciBhIGNvbmRpdGlvbiB3aXRoIGFuIHVua25vd24gY2F1c2Ugb3IgcGF0aG9waHlzaW9sb2d5LjwvcD4=\" id=\"L8b301482e67c885e74ca41ae6f0d1f5c\" data-source=\"L8b301482e67c885e74ca41ae6f0d1f5c\">idiopathic</span> autoimmune disease <span class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"api explanation\" data-type=\"bonus\" data-content=\"\" id=\"Efd72030b6f138f8394eb57b4a5405575\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li>May be associated with: <span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"K_dU6s0\" data-page=\"902–907.e1\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"1\">[1]</span><ul>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"pwcLPe0\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z6709f19b0cddb8847d2d6ffe04719c2b\" data-learningcard-id=\"Vu0GJ3\" data-lxid=\"Vu0GJ3\" data-title=\"SWdHNC1yZWxhdGVkIGRpc2Vhc2U=\" id=\"Lada4f621d0230058d3eda3555352cdaa\" data-source=\"Lada4f621d0230058d3eda3555352cdaa\">IgG4-related disease</span></li>\n<li>\n<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"X4093T\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zc64734d27e0566123d42edaf0faad254\" data-learningcard-id=\"uu0pG3\" data-lxid=\"uu0pG3\" data-title=\"TWV0YWJvbGljIHN5bmRyb21l\" id=\"Ld945b8395d0a62289cececb5b3a3fe2d\" data-source=\"Ld945b8395d0a62289cececb5b3a3fe2d\">Metabolic syndrome</span> and <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"Rs0luh\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"\" id=\"Lfafd2c2a8823f4a49668f16ee57c7928\" data-source=\"Lfafd2c2a8823f4a49668f16ee57c7928\">obesity</span>\n</li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"qv0CaR\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z4cf8ac74cb57d3c309449ff2e7c9611f\" data-learningcard-id=\"DS01bf\" data-lxid=\"DS01bf\" data-title=\"Q29yb25hcnkgYXJ0ZXJ5IGRpc2Vhc2U=\" id=\"L522a1e873ce97802b69164374303d639\" data-source=\"L522a1e873ce97802b69164374303d639\">Coronary artery disease</span></li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"T406iT\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z45c7ff4091f4118f9a1659cdec6c8bdd\" data-learningcard-id=\"qg0Cw2\" data-lxid=\"qg0Cw2\" data-title=\"TmVwaHJvbGl0aGlhc2lz\" id=\"Ld53359599ab3b17dcb534c104b09401a\" data-source=\"Ld53359599ab3b17dcb534c104b09401a\">Urolithiasis</span></li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"2oWTYm0\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z69d84d36a6a40eb875c877624d34e023\" data-learningcard-id=\"qM0Cpg\" data-lxid=\"qM0Cpg\" data-section-id=\"15c2Q10\" data-sxid=\"15c2Q10\" data-title=\"SW1tdW5vc3VwcHJlc3NhbnRzIOKGkiBCaW9sb2dpY2FsIGFnZW50cyB1c2VkIGluIGltbXVub3RoZXJhcHk=\" id=\"L139c22e2175a5c374c36eecfeea55ae0\" data-source=\"L139c22e2175a5c374c36eecfeea55ae0\">Immune checkpoint inhibitors</span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<!--no-condensed--><p class=\"condensed-hidden\">Patients are often asymptomatic.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Y0c138567a88dbe0654f443ed8b4c1f22\" class=\"condensed-hidden\">Common features <span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"K_dU6s0\" data-page=\"902–907.e1\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"1\">[1]</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>Abdominal <span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zd673a3f7ee36023aab5a267899e984cc\" data-learningcard-id=\"xN0EWg\" data-lxid=\"xN0EWg\" data-section-id=\"NBX-a00\" data-sxid=\"NBX-a00\" data-title=\"UHJpbmNpcGxlcyBvZiBwYWluIG1hbmFnZW1lbnQg4oaSIENsYXNzaWZpY2F0aW9uIG9mIHBhaW4=\" id=\"L9c5cea5adedabae6f39955e1c4ca78a6\" data-source=\"L9c5cea5adedabae6f39955e1c4ca78a6\">pain</span> (most common)</li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"AQXRAB\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"\" id=\"La2c7cb780e574f89bf365f36f4144763\" data-source=\"La2c7cb780e574f89bf365f36f4144763\">Bloating</span></li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"ro0fWS\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z51b67b2885f849894721232a6bf6d273\" data-learningcard-id=\"6M0jpg\" data-lxid=\"6M0jpg\" data-title=\"RGlhcnJoZWE=\" id=\"La9f85c4515e75350c0e88d5994964e0a\" data-source=\"La9f85c4515e75350c0e88d5994964e0a\">Diarrhea</span></li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"9DYNgr\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z65fd66f9cecf14d85a69e656c3a69417\" data-learningcard-id=\"CM0qIg\" data-lxid=\"CM0qIg\" data-title=\"Q29uc3RpcGF0aW9u\" id=\"L40867491bfecc14bc87abc3fbdbbe1de\" data-source=\"L40867491bfecc14bc87abc3fbdbbe1de\">Constipation</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z2f0b48ef2acaab783b03e4c8d2404f90\" data-learningcard-id=\"7J04vS\" data-lxid=\"7J04vS\" data-title=\"TmF1c2VhIGFuZCB2b21pdGluZw==\" id=\"L7d10d0aaa25f3ebbdbda6072f3885d65\" data-source=\"L7d10d0aaa25f3ebbdbda6072f3885d65\">Nausea and vomiting</span></li>\n<li>Weight loss</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"Y1e29aab4d92e1093a907283ba8fcbf5d\" class=\"condensed-hidden\">Features of severe disease <span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"K_dU6s0\" data-page=\"902–907.e1\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"1\">[1]</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>\n<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"2O0T7T\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zd632dab0bd82fad268f38b319729e1c3\" data-learningcard-id=\"230T3f\" data-lxid=\"230T3f\" data-title=\"Qm93ZWwgb2JzdHJ1Y3Rpb24=\" id=\"L182cfbd010e46a1c7a7ff09132e5d183\" data-source=\"L182cfbd010e46a1c7a7ff09132e5d183\">Bowel obstruction</span> or <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"WQ0PEf\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zbc05e544d46e794a60ac9ce9ec6883af\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-lxid=\"VP0GdT\" data-section-id=\"k9cmne0\" data-sxid=\"k9cmne0\" data-title=\"Q2VsbHVsYXIgY2hhbmdlcyBhbmQgYWRhcHRpdmUgcmVzcG9uc2VzIOKGkiBJc2NoZW1pYQ==\" id=\"L69639178b1e1f15cccfa42967c1f8abf\" data-source=\"L69639178b1e1f15cccfa42967c1f8abf\">ischemia</span>\n</li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"ZpcZLW0\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z9bde7e365831576405389dbed7a4e857\" data-learningcard-id=\"cS0aA2\" data-lxid=\"cS0aA2\" data-section-id=\"xScEbX0\" data-sxid=\"xScEbX0\" data-title=\"SW50ZXN0aW5hbCBpc2NoZW1pYSDihpIgQWN1dGUgbWVzZW50ZXJpYyBpc2NoZW1pYQ==\" id=\"L6f14f853c334e19acffcac2a2cb9da8b\" data-source=\"L6f14f853c334e19acffcac2a2cb9da8b\">Mesenteric venous thrombosis</span></li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"YNan-k\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zb3de189fac0d57eac5b7798e127a5e19\" data-learningcard-id=\"xm0E3g\" data-lxid=\"xm0E3g\" data-title=\"U2Vwc2lz\" id=\"L4230ddafb9e5328e464573c51aeb7351\" data-source=\"L4230ddafb9e5328e464573c51aeb7351\">Sepsis</span></li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"qF0CQ3\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Ze4c0f2bc5d18822b8df0aca961ece730\" data-learningcard-id=\"0S0ey2\" data-lxid=\"0S0ey2\" data-section-id=\"iRdJ5p0\" data-sxid=\"iRdJ5p0\" data-title=\"TWFsYWJzb3JwdGlvbiDihpIgQ29tcGxpY2F0aW9ucw==\" id=\"Lf3659e932f566a7d547a916547f9d92e\" data-source=\"Lf3659e932f566a7d547a916547f9d92e\">Protein-losing enteropathy</span></li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"qQ1CCg0\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zbdc3b2167c4bab75e0f1bf58faab9e22\" data-learningcard-id=\"lg0vv2\" data-lxid=\"lg0vv2\" data-section-id=\"l70vNh\" data-sxid=\"l70vNh\" data-title=\"Q2hyb25pYyByZW5hbCBmYWlsdXJl\" id=\"L4e4506e9e8b569729010e080ebaa9478\" data-source=\"L4e4506e9e8b569729010e080ebaa9478\">Renal failure</span></li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"_405NT\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z48e76ffce1b364c1ba4dacdd79a56b7b\" data-learningcard-id=\"KS0U0f\" data-lxid=\"KS0U0f\" data-title=\"QXNjaXRlcw==\" id=\"L08b2c7b3c729199132fcbb2263013433\" data-source=\"L08b2c7b3c729199132fcbb2263013433\">Ascites</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<!--no-condensed--><h2 id=\"Y704f86d25c69e37b4e7411d5adeb2a63\" class=\"condensed-hidden\">General principles <span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"K_dU6s0\" data-page=\"902–907.e1\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"1\">[1]</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>\n<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"1S02A2\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QSBwYXRob2xvZ2ljYWwgaGFyZGVuaW5nIG9mIHRpc3N1ZSBhcyBhIHJlc3VsdCBvZiBhbiBpbmZsYW1tYXRvcnkgb3IgYSBkZWdlbmVyYXRpdmUgcHJvY2Vzcy4gQ2hhcmFjdGVyaXplZCBoaXN0b2xvZ2ljYWxseSBieSBhbiBpbmNyZWFzZSBpbiB0aGUgbGV2ZWwgb2YgY29sbGFnZW4gYW5kL29yIHJldGljdWxpbi48L3A+\" id=\"Lead9c8d5c0001b4f259880ede0b5e231\" data-source=\"Lead9c8d5c0001b4f259880ede0b5e231\">Sclerosing</span> mesenteritis is most often an incidental finding on CT.</li>\n<li>Rule out alternative diagnoses.</li>\n<li>A presumptive diagnosis can often be made based on characteristic imaging findings.</li>\n<li>\n<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"sebtZG\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+VGhlIHJlbW92YWwgb2YgY2VsbHMgb3IgdGlzc3VlIGZvciBsYWJvcmF0b3J5IGV4YW1pbmF0aW9uIG9yIHRlc3RpbmcuIFNldmVyYWwgbWV0aG9kcyBleGlzdCB0byByZW1vdmUgdGhlIHRhcmdldCB0aXNzdWUgKGUuZy4sIGZpbmUgbmVlZGxlIGFzcGlyYXRpb24sIHB1bmNoIGJpb3BzeSkuPC9wPg==\" id=\"L95cdb0c6393ad3d5982c6c4116756d6b\" data-source=\"L95cdb0c6393ad3d5982c6c4116756d6b\">Biopsy</span> is not typically required if imaging findings are characteristic and there are no <span class=\"nowrap\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"tI0Xeh\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zfb6f18bd1a90e6210c6c195344e22cb0\" data-learningcard-id=\"mT0Vr2\" data-lxid=\"mT0Vr2\" data-section-id=\"6m0jgg\" data-sxid=\"6m0jgg\" data-title=\"SG9kZ2tpbiBseW1waG9tYSDihpIgQ2xpbmljYWwgZmVhdHVyZXM=\" id=\"Lfa8aed1382b9875f8999fb8ee47f9d5b\" data-source=\"Lfa8aed1382b9875f8999fb8ee47f9d5b\">B symptoms</span></span>.</li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Ze58aa99e36800145f14fde1821e34632\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-lxid=\"Ln0wFg\" data-title=\"TGFib3JhdG9yeSBtZWRpY2luZQ==\" id=\"L7f1862bf6288f81624c838129f8b9b8f\" data-source=\"L7f1862bf6288f81624c838129f8b9b8f\">Laboratory studies</span> may show nonspecific findings.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"Y33e2aff9fd6a68b516b26665f521c30a\" class=\"condensed-hidden\">Abdominal CT <span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"K_dU6s0\" data-page=\"902–907.e1\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"1\">[1]</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>\n<span class=\"nowrap\">≥ 3</span> of the following findings suggest <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"1S02A2\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QSBwYXRob2xvZ2ljYWwgaGFyZGVuaW5nIG9mIHRpc3N1ZSBhcyBhIHJlc3VsdCBvZiBhbiBpbmZsYW1tYXRvcnkgb3IgYSBkZWdlbmVyYXRpdmUgcHJvY2Vzcy4gQ2hhcmFjdGVyaXplZCBoaXN0b2xvZ2ljYWxseSBieSBhbiBpbmNyZWFzZSBpbiB0aGUgbGV2ZWwgb2YgY29sbGFnZW4gYW5kL29yIHJldGljdWxpbi48L3A+\" id=\"L45a0895b19a49a1e694ea1ec1e3dcef8\" data-source=\"L45a0895b19a49a1e694ea1ec1e3dcef8\">sclerosing</span> mesenteritis:<ul>\n<li>Intestine displaced by a hazy fat mass in the <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"xjXEcy\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z2e7145689ecdf9560060a209d9ae676a\" data-learningcard-id=\"LJ0wuS\" data-lxid=\"LJ0wuS\" data-section-id=\"Ja1sl20\" data-sxid=\"Ja1sl20\" data-title=\"QWJkb21pbmFsIGNhdml0eSDihpIgUGVyaXRvbmV1bQ==\" id=\"Lbdf5fb08d1b7752933bc0015fcbba830\" data-source=\"Lbdf5fb08d1b7752933bc0015fcbba830\">mesentery</span> (misty <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"xjXEcy\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z2e7145689ecdf9560060a209d9ae676a\" data-learningcard-id=\"LJ0wuS\" data-lxid=\"LJ0wuS\" data-section-id=\"Ja1sl20\" data-sxid=\"Ja1sl20\" data-title=\"QWJkb21pbmFsIGNhdml0eSDihpIgUGVyaXRvbmV1bQ==\" id=\"L3a98202fc46ea826e5ea46f4072a0d4a\" data-source=\"L3a98202fc46ea826e5ea46f4072a0d4a\">mesentery</span>)</li>\n<li>Nonenhancing perimesenteric fat with higher attenuation than adjacent <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"xjXEcy\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z2e7145689ecdf9560060a209d9ae676a\" data-learningcard-id=\"LJ0wuS\" data-lxid=\"LJ0wuS\" data-section-id=\"Ja1sl20\" data-sxid=\"Ja1sl20\" data-title=\"QWJkb21pbmFsIGNhdml0eSDihpIgUGVyaXRvbmV1bQ==\" id=\"L4d5bcb02d7c440edc1f5e6c0a8a72a39\" data-source=\"L4d5bcb02d7c440edc1f5e6c0a8a72a39\">mesentery</span>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"xjXEcy\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z2e7145689ecdf9560060a209d9ae676a\" data-learningcard-id=\"LJ0wuS\" data-lxid=\"LJ0wuS\" data-section-id=\"Ja1sl20\" data-sxid=\"Ja1sl20\" data-title=\"QWJkb21pbmFsIGNhdml0eSDihpIgUGVyaXRvbmV1bQ==\" id=\"Lca02d4c471230de3842c386f93395cd0\" data-source=\"Lca02d4c471230de3842c386f93395cd0\">Mesenteric</span> <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"yhXdgB\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z5fb5bd23c6255d2e24514ab1610448ae\" data-learningcard-id=\"960NMS\" data-lxid=\"960NMS\" data-section-id=\"ZEcZ8V0\" data-sxid=\"ZEcZ8V0\" data-title=\"THltcGhhdGljIHN5c3RlbSDihpIgU2Vjb25kYXJ5IGx5bXBoYXRpYyBvcmdhbnM=\" id=\"Lcf20db820513aba5112e833abdba5737\" data-source=\"Lcf20db820513aba5112e833abdba5737\">lymph nodes</span> <span class=\"nowrap\">&lt; 1 cm</span>\n</li>\n<li>Hypoattenuated halo around the central vessels</li>\n<li>Thin, surrounding <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"yi0d8f\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zf29b9e7e01bf75d0402e969b50992d30\" data-learningcard-id=\"ro0fWS\" data-lxid=\"ro0fWS\" data-section-id=\"H9cKKe0\" data-sxid=\"H9cKKe0\" data-title=\"Q29ubmVjdGl2ZSB0aXNzdWUg4oaSIENsaW5pY2FsIHNpZ25pZmljYW5jZQ==\" id=\"Lc952d5fcce388c6d0a15e85f1407dbdc\" data-source=\"Lc952d5fcce388c6d0a15e85f1407dbdc\">fibrotic</span> <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"r7VfMD0\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QSBsYXllciBvZiB0aXNzdWUgdGhhdCBzdXJyb3VuZHMgYSBsZXNpb24gKGUuZy4sIGEgdHVtb3IpIGJ1dCBpcyBub3QgYSB0cnVlIGNhcHN1bGUgZm9ybWVkIGJ5IHRoZSBsZXNpb24gaXRzZWxmLjwvcD4=\" id=\"Lc092365a37f50cefd999cbac6ad539c3\" data-source=\"Lc092365a37f50cefd999cbac6ad539c3\">pseudocapsule</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Calcifications and retractions of the bowel may suggest severe disease and/or <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"OHXIqz\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z8c3bce39ca977e0f872b6d9fb3be8cfb\" data-learningcard-id=\"WM0Png\" data-lxid=\"WM0Png\" data-section-id=\"azXQr00\" data-sxid=\"azXQr00\" data-title=\"R2VuZXJhbCBvbmNvbG9neSDihpIgTm9tZW5jbGF0dXJl\" id=\"L64c8a722c09c43e9569d7e4d654ae761\" data-source=\"L64c8a722c09c43e9569d7e4d654ae761\">malignancy</span>.</li>\n<li>Findings in patients with <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"pwcLPe0\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z6709f19b0cddb8847d2d6ffe04719c2b\" data-learningcard-id=\"Vu0GJ3\" data-lxid=\"Vu0GJ3\" data-title=\"SWdHNC1yZWxhdGVkIGRpc2Vhc2U=\" id=\"Lf52ce2294c07f0647d0fd825dc82557d\" data-source=\"Lf52ce2294c07f0647d0fd825dc82557d\">IgG4-related disease</span> may be atypical (e.g., multiple large <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"yhXdgB\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z5fb5bd23c6255d2e24514ab1610448ae\" data-learningcard-id=\"960NMS\" data-lxid=\"960NMS\" data-section-id=\"ZEcZ8V0\" data-sxid=\"ZEcZ8V0\" data-title=\"THltcGhhdGljIHN5c3RlbSDihpIgU2Vjb25kYXJ5IGx5bXBoYXRpYyBvcmdhbnM=\" id=\"L589f361e07449c1513efde4dc2a8bbb5\" data-source=\"L589f361e07449c1513efde4dc2a8bbb5\">lymph nodes</span>, apparent local invasion of organs).</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"Yc33fda7776d10583c51b545149e512f2\" class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Ze58aa99e36800145f14fde1821e34632\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-lxid=\"Ln0wFg\" data-title=\"TGFib3JhdG9yeSBtZWRpY2luZQ==\" id=\"L3fb8b6378fe66b88819d93fddf4621d3\" data-source=\"L3fb8b6378fe66b88819d93fddf4621d3\">Laboratory studies</span> <span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"K_dU6s0\" data-page=\"902–907.e1\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"1\">[1]</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>\n<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"LVYwEL\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zde306dd72fd9fa8f94347d3f2edafc20\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-lxid=\"Ln0wFg\" data-section-id=\"-V1DCf0\" data-sxid=\"-V1DCf0\" data-title=\"TGFib3JhdG9yeSBtZWRpY2luZSDihpIgSW5mbGFtbWF0b3J5IG1hcmtlcnM=\" id=\"La31f6529349a924fc62c47a91dfcf15e\" data-source=\"La31f6529349a924fc62c47a91dfcf15e\">ESR</span> and <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"IVYYDL\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z51ad1e101a45a8de708a6dda0321755d\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-lxid=\"Ln0wFg\" data-section-id=\"-V1DCf0\" data-sxid=\"-V1DCf0\" data-title=\"TGFib3JhdG9yeSBtZWRpY2luZSDihpIgSW5mbGFtbWF0b3J5IG1hcmtlcnM=\" id=\"La6b4f30965aed1a2cce724f6d7c6dcbb\" data-source=\"La6b4f30965aed1a2cce724f6d7c6dcbb\">CRP</span>: may be elevated</li>\n<li>Serum IgG4: elevated in <span class=\"nowrap\">∼ 50%</span> of patients with IgG4-related <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"1S02A2\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QSBwYXRob2xvZ2ljYWwgaGFyZGVuaW5nIG9mIHRpc3N1ZSBhcyBhIHJlc3VsdCBvZiBhbiBpbmZsYW1tYXRvcnkgb3IgYSBkZWdlbmVyYXRpdmUgcHJvY2Vzcy4gQ2hhcmFjdGVyaXplZCBoaXN0b2xvZ2ljYWxseSBieSBhbiBpbmNyZWFzZSBpbiB0aGUgbGV2ZWwgb2YgY29sbGFnZW4gYW5kL29yIHJldGljdWxpbi48L3A+\" id=\"Lf6d27bd633d5dbba2a8701ce002b0b7a\" data-source=\"Lf6d27bd633d5dbba2a8701ce002b0b7a\">sclerosing</span> mesenteritis</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"Yae115e82aa59fdf9dd402c1dcf01145a\" class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"sebtZG\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+VGhlIHJlbW92YWwgb2YgY2VsbHMgb3IgdGlzc3VlIGZvciBsYWJvcmF0b3J5IGV4YW1pbmF0aW9uIG9yIHRlc3RpbmcuIFNldmVyYWwgbWV0aG9kcyBleGlzdCB0byByZW1vdmUgdGhlIHRhcmdldCB0aXNzdWUgKGUuZy4sIGZpbmUgbmVlZGxlIGFzcGlyYXRpb24sIHB1bmNoIGJpb3BzeSkuPC9wPg==\" id=\"Lf3d842b8e0f6f57d8424fcb55eb6ad0f\" data-source=\"Lf3d842b8e0f6f57d8424fcb55eb6ad0f\">Biopsy</span> <span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"K_dU6s0\" data-page=\"902–907.e1\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"1\">[1]</span></h2>\n<p class=\"condensed-hidden\">Indications for <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"sebtZG\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+VGhlIHJlbW92YWwgb2YgY2VsbHMgb3IgdGlzc3VlIGZvciBsYWJvcmF0b3J5IGV4YW1pbmF0aW9uIG9yIHRlc3RpbmcuIFNldmVyYWwgbWV0aG9kcyBleGlzdCB0byByZW1vdmUgdGhlIHRhcmdldCB0aXNzdWUgKGUuZy4sIGZpbmUgbmVlZGxlIGFzcGlyYXRpb24sIHB1bmNoIGJpb3BzeSkuPC9wPg==\" id=\"L130c181d1fba1ea21ac0b4a3ff9d62d2\" data-source=\"L130c181d1fba1ea21ac0b4a3ff9d62d2\">biopsy</span> include:</p>\n<ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>CT findings with signs of malignant <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"OCYIHr\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z9a24d08ab67dee43098222189f24cc1a\" data-learningcard-id=\"iL0Jxg\" data-lxid=\"iL0Jxg\" data-title=\"THltcGhhZGVub3BhdGh5\" id=\"L5ac56bb7638c48625f8f9942730acd2a\" data-source=\"L5ac56bb7638c48625f8f9942730acd2a\">lymphadenopathy</span>, e.g.:<ul>\n<li>\n<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"OCYIHr\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z9a24d08ab67dee43098222189f24cc1a\" data-learningcard-id=\"iL0Jxg\" data-lxid=\"iL0Jxg\" data-title=\"THltcGhhZGVub3BhdGh5\" id=\"L93cf50e54c1095e4923100678dc0c3d3\" data-source=\"L93cf50e54c1095e4923100678dc0c3d3\">Lymphadenopathy</span> with <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"yhXdgB\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z5fb5bd23c6255d2e24514ab1610448ae\" data-learningcard-id=\"960NMS\" data-lxid=\"960NMS\" data-section-id=\"ZEcZ8V0\" data-sxid=\"ZEcZ8V0\" data-title=\"THltcGhhdGljIHN5c3RlbSDihpIgU2Vjb25kYXJ5IGx5bXBoYXRpYyBvcmdhbnM=\" id=\"L27ee2cb6ef35d0933a7606f09109ba3b\" data-source=\"L27ee2cb6ef35d0933a7606f09109ba3b\">lymph nodes</span> <span class=\"nowrap\">&gt; 1 cm</span>\n</li>\n<li>Concerning appearance of <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"yhXdgB\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z5fb5bd23c6255d2e24514ab1610448ae\" data-learningcard-id=\"960NMS\" data-lxid=\"960NMS\" data-section-id=\"ZEcZ8V0\" data-sxid=\"ZEcZ8V0\" data-title=\"THltcGhhdGljIHN5c3RlbSDihpIgU2Vjb25kYXJ5IGx5bXBoYXRpYyBvcmdhbnM=\" id=\"L5544872e4ed0a9b5a5aef5ee673daa7d\" data-source=\"L5544872e4ed0a9b5a5aef5ee673daa7d\">lymph nodes</span> (e.g., <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"O8aI5m\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z28b2cd3d009fe208ee54280c99b41b38\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-lxid=\"VP0GdT\" data-section-id=\"R9clMe0\" data-sxid=\"R9clMe0\" data-title=\"Q2VsbHVsYXIgY2hhbmdlcyBhbmQgYWRhcHRpdmUgcmVzcG9uc2VzIOKGkiBOZWNyb3Npcw==\" id=\"L32639934557b09405d1524f78902664b\" data-source=\"L32639934557b09405d1524f78902664b\">necrosis</span>, calcification)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Suspected <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"pwcLPe0\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z6709f19b0cddb8847d2d6ffe04719c2b\" data-learningcard-id=\"Vu0GJ3\" data-lxid=\"Vu0GJ3\" data-title=\"SWdHNC1yZWxhdGVkIGRpc2Vhc2U=\" id=\"L93719370452821fdafbafeaac74c5b0b\" data-source=\"L93719370452821fdafbafeaac74c5b0b\">IgG4-related disease</span> (to confirm the diagnosis and exclude <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"OHXIqz\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z8c3bce39ca977e0f872b6d9fb3be8cfb\" data-learningcard-id=\"WM0Png\" data-lxid=\"WM0Png\" data-section-id=\"azXQr00\" data-sxid=\"azXQr00\" data-title=\"R2VuZXJhbCBvbmNvbG9neSDihpIgTm9tZW5jbGF0dXJl\" id=\"L1823f38452bc72035e921fde8cf60a1a\" data-source=\"L1823f38452bc72035e921fde8cf60a1a\">malignancy</span>)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<!--no-condensed--><ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"mP0V2T\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z46cc87b0bb6d0dccc4fedce8fd20de06\" data-learningcard-id=\"NT0-I2\" data-lxid=\"NT0-I2\" data-title=\"Tm9uLUhvZGdraW4gbHltcGhvbWFz\" id=\"Ldcf7f22dbfc97867e1110a377bf4083a\" data-source=\"Ldcf7f22dbfc97867e1110a377bf4083a\">Non-Hodgkin lymphoma</span></li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"YgbnFG\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z308dcf5539d19f810cbb10d7cd86dfd4\" data-learningcard-id=\"TS06_2\" data-lxid=\"TS06_2\" data-section-id=\"BF1z4i0\" data-sxid=\"BF1z4i0\" data-title=\"Q29sb3JlY3RhbCBjYW5jZXIg4oaSIENvbXBsaWNhdGlvbnM=\" id=\"Le14e7ba6c51b29ac4de6a7a6da79999e\" data-source=\"Le14e7ba6c51b29ac4de6a7a6da79999e\">Peritoneal carcinomatosis</span></li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"-k0DqT\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z0184e219238691f4847f7e148d445eb4\" data-learningcard-id=\"bu0Hp3\" data-lxid=\"bu0Hp3\" data-section-id=\"fOdk7J0\" data-sxid=\"fOdk7J0\" data-title=\"TmV1cm9lbmRvY3JpbmUgbmVvcGxhc21zIOKGkiBEZWZpbml0aW9ucw==\" id=\"L31eda31bc3df9ff934945fbd5b933cbe\" data-source=\"L31eda31bc3df9ff934945fbd5b933cbe\">Carcinoid tumor</span></li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"kEbmDv\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z6e25cd984dbde29195c02a1e949c4f92\" data-learningcard-id=\"ts0X9h\" data-lxid=\"ts0X9h\" data-title=\"RGVzbW9pZCB0dW1vcnM=\" id=\"L60a5c53b04506a4a3d401381bc5e100b\" data-source=\"L60a5c53b04506a4a3d401381bc5e100b\">Desmoid tumor</span></li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"I7VYMD0\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"\" id=\"La6087781226463730af01389181b6370\" data-source=\"La6087781226463730af01389181b6370\">Encapsulating peritoneal sclerosis</span></li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"0CYeqr\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z03f0142bdc8116a585676a7b55dcd8cb\" data-learningcard-id=\"9h0NTf\" data-lxid=\"9h0NTf\" data-title=\"UmV0cm9wZXJpdG9uZWFsIGZpYnJvc2lz\" id=\"L87a62ff870dd74c2ef3ee8e1338420ea\" data-source=\"L87a62ff870dd74c2ef3ee8e1338420ea\">Retroperitoneal fibrosis</span></li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"QTauqP\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z835105c91683deba55cb3e34a57066a0\" data-learningcard-id=\"XF09g3\" data-lxid=\"XF09g3\" data-section-id=\"yEWdyM0\" data-sxid=\"yEWdyM0\" data-title=\"T3ZlcnZpZXcgb2Ygb3ZhcmlhbiB0dW1vcnMg4oaSIEVwaXRoZWxpYWwgb3ZhcmlhbiB0dW1vcnM=\" id=\"L6247a4f61d06f998566fa932b9632a98\" data-source=\"L6247a4f61d06f998566fa932b9632a98\">Pseudomyxoma peritonei</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"unwichtig\">The differential diagnoses listed here are not exhaustive.</span></p>\n<!--no-condensed--><h2 id=\"Y4132abeeb164bda2212f8031ca69f2ff\" class=\"condensed-hidden\">General principles <span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"K_dU6s0\" data-page=\"902–907.e1\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"1\">[1]</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>Patients should be managed by specialists (e.g., gastroenterologists).</li>\n<li>Start medical therapy for symptomatic patients.</li>\n<li>Offer symptomatic treatment (e.g., <span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z793f00758f040cb2cf87f540d94a2cfa\" data-learningcard-id=\"CM0qIg\" data-lxid=\"CM0qIg\" data-section-id=\"bU1HbT0\" data-sxid=\"bU1HbT0\" data-title=\"Q29uc3RpcGF0aW9uIOKGkiBUcmVhdG1lbnQ=\" id=\"L3a241f51ff52ec4379e7e05ef7730340\" data-source=\"L3a241f51ff52ec4379e7e05ef7730340\">management of constipation</span>).</li>\n<li>Provide <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"2ycTeU0\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QSBtYW5hZ2VtZW50IHN0cmF0ZWd5IHRoYXQgaW52b2x2ZXMgc2VyaWFsIGNsaW5pY2FsIG1vbml0b3JpbmcgKGkuZS4sIGludGVybWl0dGVudCBzY3JlZW5pbmcgZm9yIHN5bXB0b21zIG9mIGRpc2Vhc2UpLjwvcD4=\" id=\"L7a2206ce69fc38fd1cfb0ab818b4ed3a\" data-source=\"L7a2206ce69fc38fd1cfb0ab818b4ed3a\">expectant management</span> for asymptomatic patients; consider annual CT or <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"8n0OEg\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zefb6206a3f821bf7e5942b654dc6f6cf\" data-learningcard-id=\"pN0LXg\" data-lxid=\"pN0LXg\" data-title=\"TWFnbmV0aWMgcmVzb25hbmNlIGltYWdpbmc=\" id=\"L3e819609aa0a2400d47f1572091a6134\" data-source=\"L3e819609aa0a2400d47f1572091a6134\">MRI</span> for <span class=\"nowrap\">2 years</span> to monitor for progression.</li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Za68e01313423572283ce418087f356cb\" data-learningcard-id=\"7I04Vh\" data-lxid=\"7I04Vh\" data-section-id=\"w41hlS0\" data-sxid=\"w41hlS0\" data-title=\"U3VyZ2VyeSBjbGVya3NoaXAg4oaSIFN1cmdlcnkgb3ZlcnZpZXc=\" id=\"Lf6caa77357dc615da8b19e5f397f0ab6\" data-source=\"Lf6caa77357dc615da8b19e5f397f0ab6\">Surgery</span> may be indicated for patients with <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"2O0T7T\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zd632dab0bd82fad268f38b319729e1c3\" data-learningcard-id=\"230T3f\" data-lxid=\"230T3f\" data-title=\"Qm93ZWwgb2JzdHJ1Y3Rpb24=\" id=\"Le013fc2392854264176f4e1e1dbca86c\" data-source=\"Le013fc2392854264176f4e1e1dbca86c\">bowel obstruction</span>, but it is not curative.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"Y4a262ec8af42c068347b993ad21676e7\" class=\"condensed-hidden\">Pharmacological treatment <span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"K_dU6s0\" data-page=\"902–907.e1\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"1\">[1]</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>Preferred agents include:<ul>\n<li>\n<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"3faSNP\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z62c2028efe014cd4faaf82ccb312cd4c\" data-learningcard-id=\"uk0ppT\" data-lxid=\"uk0ppT\" data-section-id=\"a_1Q5j0\" data-sxid=\"a_1Q5j0\" data-title=\"RmVtYWxlIHNleCBob3Jtb25lcyDihpIgUmVwcm9kdWN0aXZlIHN5c3RlbSBkcnVncw==\" id=\"L6a1493d1ebad2c91f4e3fefab7ec510e\" data-source=\"L6a1493d1ebad2c91f4e3fefab7ec510e\">Tamoxifen</span> (with or without <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"YOanIk\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z7acc6b8a4fb3eecc9bdffe7ff1f88c25\" data-learningcard-id=\"km0mfg\" data-lxid=\"km0mfg\" data-section-id=\"F8bgov\" data-sxid=\"F8bgov\" data-title=\"R2x1Y29jb3J0aWNvaWRzIOKGkiBPdmVydmlldyAoT0xEL0RydWcp\" id=\"L023f4df02d585b48f8d8b37fe4acea8b\" data-source=\"L023f4df02d585b48f8d8b37fe4acea8b\">prednisone</span>): most commonly used</li>\n<li>\n<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"8J0ODS\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Za7ec01fa067126441bfca71d4f27200f\" data-learningcard-id=\"YT0n62\" data-lxid=\"YT0n62\" data-section-id=\"NJ1-830\" data-sxid=\"NJ1-830\" data-title=\"R291dCBhbmQgaHlwZXJ1cmljZW1pYSDihpIgQWN1dGUgZ291dCBmbGFyZQ==\" id=\"L81a53a01966f3eab50251d34818261e7\" data-source=\"L81a53a01966f3eab50251d34818261e7\">Colchicine</span> with <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"YOanIk\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z7acc6b8a4fb3eecc9bdffe7ff1f88c25\" data-learningcard-id=\"km0mfg\" data-lxid=\"km0mfg\" data-section-id=\"F8bgov\" data-sxid=\"F8bgov\" data-title=\"R2x1Y29jb3J0aWNvaWRzIOKGkiBPdmVydmlldyAoT0xEL0RydWcp\" id=\"Laae8f965e2c0f390aac0304808977ff3\" data-source=\"Laae8f965e2c0f390aac0304808977ff3\">prednisone</span>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"g5aFjO\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z826df053927ec3e8abd5d55515708e41\" data-learningcard-id=\"qM0Cpg\" data-lxid=\"qM0Cpg\" data-section-id=\"2eXTyC\" data-sxid=\"2eXTyC\" data-title=\"SW1tdW5vc3VwcHJlc3NhbnRzIOKGkiBPdmVydmlldyAoT0xEL0RydWcp\" id=\"L427674302bee6a05c298a857330a1018\" data-source=\"L427674302bee6a05c298a857330a1018\">Azathioprine</span> with <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"YOanIk\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z7acc6b8a4fb3eecc9bdffe7ff1f88c25\" data-learningcard-id=\"km0mfg\" data-lxid=\"km0mfg\" data-section-id=\"F8bgov\" data-sxid=\"F8bgov\" data-title=\"R2x1Y29jb3J0aWNvaWRzIOKGkiBPdmVydmlldyAoT0xEL0RydWcp\" id=\"Lecbc11bd97287b598773b0eb308a8110\" data-source=\"Lecbc11bd97287b598773b0eb308a8110\">prednisone</span>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"YOanIk\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z7acc6b8a4fb3eecc9bdffe7ff1f88c25\" data-learningcard-id=\"km0mfg\" data-lxid=\"km0mfg\" data-section-id=\"F8bgov\" data-sxid=\"F8bgov\" data-title=\"R2x1Y29jb3J0aWNvaWRzIOKGkiBPdmVydmlldyAoT0xEL0RydWcp\" id=\"Lf5c33df88000f6ff5628fedd35e4fc31\" data-source=\"Lf5c33df88000f6ff5628fedd35e4fc31\">Prednisone</span> monotherapy for short-term use <span class=\"api explanation\" data-type=\"bonus\" data-content=\"\" id=\"Eefa764656f786fcdfbab2d6e62cb7e4a\"></span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Alternative agents (e.g., <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"P5aW4O\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Ze00b1d8151bfbc4dd3b134e0567b0d43\" data-learningcard-id=\"qM0Cpg\" data-lxid=\"qM0Cpg\" data-section-id=\"15c2Q10\" data-sxid=\"15c2Q10\" data-title=\"SW1tdW5vc3VwcHJlc3NhbnRzIOKGkiBCaW9sb2dpY2FsIGFnZW50cyB1c2VkIGluIGltbXVub3RoZXJhcHk=\" id=\"L805789966f0e4c9cc03f36c09d069c33\" data-source=\"L805789966f0e4c9cc03f36c09d069c33\">rituximab</span>, <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"ekax5k\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zaad24cb56b33896890f9ae55757c4363\" data-learningcard-id=\"4m03fg\" data-lxid=\"4m03fg\" data-section-id=\"4W13lf0\" data-sxid=\"4W13lf0\" data-title=\"Q2hlbW90aGVyYXBldXRpYyBhZ2VudHMg4oaSIEFsa3lsYXRpbmcgYWdlbnRz\" id=\"L1deececaff2350a3308fce86bc895af2\" data-source=\"L1deececaff2350a3308fce86bc895af2\">cyclophosphamide</span>) may be considered in severe, refractory disease.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<!--no-condensed--><ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"2O0T7T\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zd632dab0bd82fad268f38b319729e1c3\" data-learningcard-id=\"230T3f\" data-lxid=\"230T3f\" data-title=\"Qm93ZWwgb2JzdHJ1Y3Rpb24=\" id=\"Lb1f6986bcf6cb6a12425c3a35ece83b5\" data-source=\"Lb1f6986bcf6cb6a12425c3a35ece83b5\">Bowel obstruction</span></li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"tF0XP3\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zdda3dd68bdae57a6f55a9411390cbecc\" data-learningcard-id=\"cS0aA2\" data-lxid=\"cS0aA2\" data-section-id=\"BSczbX0\" data-sxid=\"BSczbX0\" data-title=\"SW50ZXN0aW5hbCBpc2NoZW1pYSDihpIgQ2hyb25pYyBtZXNlbnRlcmljIGlzY2hlbWlh\" id=\"L2e7906ce47c534d79f276c97fa1d0b1e\" data-source=\"L2e7906ce47c534d79f276c97fa1d0b1e\">Chronic mesenteric ischemia</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"unwichtig\">We list the most important complications. The selection is not exhaustive.</span></p>\n<!--no-condensed--><p class=\"condensed-hidden\">Except in the most severe cases, the majority of patients have stable disease without radiological progression after <span class=\"nowrap\">2 years</span>, regardless of whether they receive any treatment. <span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"K_dU6s0\" data-page=\"902–907.e1\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"1\">[1]</span></p>\n\n            "
}